<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٩٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3689">‌أَبُو سَعِيدٍ الْأَشَجُّ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4424">‌عُقْبَةُ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> ثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4195">‌عُبَيْدُ اللهِ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> ثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">‌نَافِعٌ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">‌ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a>رَضِيَ اللهُ عَنْهُمَا،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«طَلَّقْتُ امْرَأَتِي»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>